{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody was waiting for his date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, oh, your date is late, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said yes, would you mind waiting together?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, his date came, but my date never came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was left there in the bushes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But a-- they noticed that somebody was missing in that row.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians came looking, but at that time, I was walking with this man on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how I escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I got to this village later and spent there till the end of the war, actually.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bronkowice.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-R-O-N-K-O-W-I-C-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To this man by the name [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Novak ?] that was going to find a place for me with this little child to save him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- I stayed with-- with that family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When somebody knocked on the door, they put me into the wardrobe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- you know, in Europe, they-- you didn't have closets like you have here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have standing wardrobes, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they put me into there and closed the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I stayed there until-- until the people left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then finally he told them that he has a cousin that escaped from the Germans because they're looking for her, and he told her it's OK to come to him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So from that day on, I didn't have to hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was like in the open and known as a cousin of the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I was-- I was once outside, and the-- and the-- the people, the villagers, were working in the fields, and a man came running and he said to me, there are two Jews coming out from the forest here.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
